00:40.019 --> 00:45.008
- Well, do you mind telling me
what day it is, Chip?

00:45.010 --> 00:47.023
- It's the 10th day
of December.

00:48.001 --> 00:51.020
- Oh, shoot.
We missed it.

00:51.022 --> 00:55.005
- We missed what?
- Nothing. Forget it.

00:55.007 --> 00:57.001
- No, no, wait.
Dory, please, please tell me.

00:57.003 --> 00:58.014
What did we miss?
Please?

00:58.016 --> 01:01.014
- It's silly.
It's just...

01:01.016 --> 01:03.014
