celebrate it next year.

01:17.018 --> 01:19.010
- [sighs]

01:19.012 --> 01:22.002
Fuck!
Idiot!

01:23.009 --> 01:25.004
- Oh, well.

01:25.006 --> 01:26.012
- We can just do it now.

01:26.014 --> 01:27.023
- Yeah?
- Yeah!

01:28.001 --> 01:29.004
- Okay--
- Wait, don't eat this.

01:29.006 --> 01:30.011
I'm gonna make
something special.

01:30.013 --> 01:32.004
- Okay.
- Oh, my God.

01:32.006 --> 01:33.019
Dory, I'm so happy

01:33.021 --> 01:36.003
