since 1920.

02:27.008 --> 02:29.006
What did you pray for?
- Thank you, Charlie.

02:29.008 --> 02:30.015
That was beautiful,
first of all.

02:30.017 --> 02:31.020
- Mm-hmm.

02:31.022 --> 02:34.013
- Today, I pray
for a gay restaurant

02:34.015 --> 02:37.004
that I was booed
out of this morning.

02:37.006 --> 02:38.022
Yeah.
[scoffs]

